Life Story

A broker for the timberwright’s guild, Naviel is a follower. Reasonably intelligent, he hates to make decisions and prefers to defer to others. He is of average size, with a slim build, green eyes and brown hair. He wears good clothes that always seem a little baggy on him as if they were hand-me-downs. Naviel has no tact and bluntly says whatever comes to mind. For the last five years, he has acted as Akitt’s agent, finding buyers for the timber and investing his profits. He has an extensive array of shady and illegal contacts throughout the kingdom. He keeps one penny in seven of Akitt’s ill-gotten gains.
